<i>noun</i>: 홀어미 [호러미], 홀어머니 [호러머니], 생과부 [생과부], 미망인 [미ː망인], 과부 [과ː부] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>홀어미 [호러미]</dt><br>
<dd>widow; single mother</dd><br>
<dd>남편을 잃고 혼자 자식을 키우며 사는 여자.</dd><br>
<dd>A woman who lives alone, raising her children after having lost her husband.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>홀어머니 [호러머니]</dt><br>
<dd>widow; single mother</dd><br>
<dd>(높이는 말로) 홀어미.</dd><br>
<dd>(polite form) A widowed mother.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>생과부 [생과부]</dt><br>
<dd>1. grass widow</dd><br>
<dd>남편이 있으면서도 멀리 떨어져 있어서 과부나 다름없이 혼자 사는 여자.</dd><br>
<dd>A married woman who lives alone like a widow because her husband is far away from her.</dd><br>
<dd>2. widow</dd><br>
<dd>결혼을 했다가 남편이 죽어서 혼자 사는 여자.</dd><br>
<dd>A woman left alone after her husband's death.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>미망인 [미ː망인]</dt><br>
<dd>widow</dd><br>
<dd>남편이 죽어서 홀로 남겨진 여자.</dd><br>
<dd>A woman who has been left alone after her husband died.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>과부 [과ː부]</dt><br>
<dd>widow</dd><br>
<dd>남편이 죽고 나서 남편 없이 사는 여자.</dd><br>
<dd>A woman remaining unmarried after her husband's death.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>